Stormwatch (000 - 030) (2011 - 2014) (Digital) (Nahga-Empire+Minutemen-PhD)


New volume of Stormwatch, following the post-Flashpoint relaunch of the DC Universe. This series sees Stormwatch outside of WildStorm for the first time and was the first WildStorm property to be released under the DC banner following the closing of WildStorm in 2010. The team includes most core members of the Authority, Martian Manhunter, and a number of new characters
